    RESULT
        epm_Data    -   points to first element if sucessful.
        epm_Error will equal EPCERR_NOERR if sucessful or an error defined in
        extproc.h.

    SEE ALSO
        EPC_GETSAMPLE, EPC_GETBUFFER.


