        scanning a sound sample you could set PIMAX to the length, and
        periodically update the bars position using EPC_PIVAL.

    INPUTS
        epm_Command =   EPC_PIMAX
        epm_Data    =   pointer to a ULONG of the maximum length

    RESULT
        epm_Error will equal EPCERR_NOERR if sucessful or an error defined in
        extproc.h.

    SEE ALSO
        EPC_PICLOSE, EPC_PIOPEN, EPC_PIVAL, EPC_PISTRING,


